CENTERING A BLOCK ELEMENT
margin: 0 auto; //left and right is set by browser automaticallly

SHOWING BACKGROUND removed because of floating content
clearfix hack:
.clearfix::after {
    content: "";
    clear: both;
    display: table;
}

NOT PSEUDO SSELECTOR
-select everything except the one indicated inside paren
e.g. &:not(:last-child){
	//applies the style to everything except last-child
	margin-bottom: 40px;
}

SASS OPERATIONS
calc - allows mixed units (rem, pixels, etc..)
e.g. width: calc(100%- #{$gutter-horizontal})/2);

ATTR SELECTOR
[class^="col-"] {
	//apply style to only elements whose class name starts with col
}

MAIN element. - tells search engines that this part is the main part of the site

EMMET EXTENSION
-write html shortcut
-.className + tab = creates div with clas name
-section.classname + tab = creates section elment with classname


WEBKIT
-webkit-background-clip: text;
clip background to where text is. if text set to transparent background is seen.

